Bundesbank, Lufthansa Worker Raided Over Euro Scam, Bild Reports

-- B y   C h r i s   M a l p a s s
-- 
2011-03-31T04:35:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-31/bundesbank-lufthansa-worker-raided-over-euro-scam-bild-reports.html
German authorities raided the homes
of employees of the Bundesbank and  Deutsche Lufthansa AG (LHA)  as part
of an investigation into a scheme to exchange euro coins taken
out of circulation for bank notes, Bild Zeitung reported.      Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
